Proper Citation 
 
 
1.	The Dataset Identity 
•	Original Name: Predict Students' Dropout and Academic Success 
•	Source: Polytechnic Institute of Portalegre (Portugal) 
•	Original Publication: Published in the journal Data (2021) 
 
2.	APA Style (Standard for Reports): 
Realinho, V., Machado, J., Baptista, L., & Martins, M. V. (2021). Predict Students' Dropout and Academic Success. Data, 6(11), 146. https://doi.org/10.3390/data7110146 
 
3.	Source Acknowledgement (Transparency): 
"The dataset was accessed via Kaggle (uploaded by 'The Devastator'), which mirrors the original data from the UCI Machine Learning Repository." 
 
4.	Dataset 
•	Rows: 4,424 Students 
•	Columns: 35 Features (Demographic, Socio-economic, Macro-economic, Academic) 
•	Target Classes: 3 (Dropout, Enrolled, Graduate)  
•	Timeframe: Data covers students enrolled in various undergraduate degrees (Agronomy, Design, Nursing, etc.). 
 
 
